    <div class="faq-wrap">
      <div class="faq-item reveal"><button class="faq-btn" onclick="toggleFaq(this)"><span class="faq-btn-text">What services does New Way Consultancy offer?</span><div class="faq-ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><line x1="12" y1="5" x2="12" y2="19"/><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/></svg></div></button><div class="faq-answer">We offer a comprehensive range of career services: career counseling, resume building, interview preparation, domestic and overseas job placement, manpower supply, visa guidance, document attestation, and skill-based career planning — all from our office in Perinthalmanna.</div></div>
      <div class="faq-item reveal"><button class="faq-btn" onclick="toggleFaq(this)"><span class="faq-btn-text">How do I get started with New Way Consultancy?</span><div class="faq-ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><line x1="12" y1="5" x2="12" y2="19"/><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/></svg></div></button><div class="faq-answer">You can walk into our office at KIMS Avenue Building, Shanti Nagar, Perinthalmanna, call us at +91 80867 40392, message us on WhatsApp, or fill out the contact form on this page. We'll schedule an initial consultation to understand your background and goals.</div></div>
      <div class="faq-item reveal"><button class="faq-btn" onclick="toggleFaq(this)"><span class="faq-btn-text">Which countries do you place candidates in?</span><div class="faq-ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><line x1="12" y1="5" x2="12" y2="19"/><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/></svg></div></button><div class="faq-answer">We have successfully placed candidates across 15+ countries including UAE, Qatar, Saudi Arabia, Kuwait, Bahrain, Oman, and other Gulf destinations, as well as major cities across India including Bangalore, Mumbai, and Delhi.</div></div>
      <div class="faq-item reveal"><button class="faq-btn" onclick="toggleFaq(this)"><span class="faq-btn-text">Do you assist with visa processing and document attestation?</span><div class="faq-ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><line x1="12" y1="5" x2="12" y2="19"/><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/></svg></div></button><div class="faq-answer">Yes. We provide complete visa guidance and processing support for overseas placements and assist with educational and professional document attestation — ensuring everything is accurate, compliant, and submitted on time.</div></div>
      <div class="faq-item reveal"><button class="faq-btn" onclick="toggleFaq(this)"><span class="faq-btn-text">What are your office hours?</span><div class="faq-ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><line x1="12" y1="5" x2="12" y2="19"/><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/></svg></div></button><div class="faq-answer">Our office is open Monday to Saturday from 9:30 AM to 6:00 PM. We are closed on Sundays. You can also reach us via WhatsApp (+91 80867 40392) or email (newwaypmna@gmail.com) at any time and we will respond promptly.</div></div>
